original_font_information.description: Helvetica Now is the first comprehensive reworking of the Helvetica family in more than 35 years. It consists of three size ranges: Micro, Text and Display. Helvetica Now Text is the workhorse of the group. Its refined forms and spacing make it a pleasure to read, and its ample palette of weights (Thin to Black) make it an obvious choice for todays ultra-demanding, information-rich design environments.
